&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3959&quot; title=&quot;Golang TSimpleServer Is More Of A TThreadedServer?&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-3959&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-3959&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; explain simpleServer is not a typical TSimpleServer&lt;/p&gt;

